==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Overstrain
<hw>O`ver*strain"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To stretch or strain too
much; <as>as, to <ex>overstrain</ex> one's nerves</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Ayliffe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overstraitly</ent>⟦br⟧
